<FIRST>r f PM-BusinessHighlights 2Takes   10-06 0551</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Business Highlights, 2 Takes,0577</SECOND>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
